<br>
Get a puller who knows how to pull the zone, not train it<br>
<br>
You will need a ton of dots, and you will loose money on them in most cases<br>
<br>
Lay out the loot rules WITH the raid announcment<br>
<br>
Have a plan on what you are going to do, ie clear to SW corner of hate, then clear to organ house to camp in organ house and have puller bring the world to you...<br>
<br>
